Item.Description:
EARPOD with Volume Control Remote & Mic for iPhone 5 Touch 5  in 8 Colors (Black, White, Red, Pink, Orange, Blue, Green, and Purple)
Compatible with New iPhone 5 iPOD Touch 5 Nano 7 iPad Mini

Stylish and sensational, the in-ear headphones take your music listening experience to a whole new level. Sporting an ergonomic design, these headphones fit more comfortably in your ears, letting you enjoy music for long hours without any hassle. Equipped with a 3.5 mm connector, these in-ear headphones are compatible with iPod, iPhone, and iPad models. Coming with an mic and in-line remote control with a volume control button, answer/end button and play/pause button, the EarPods let you answer calls and control music playback without removing the phone from your pocket. What’s more, with the included storage case, you can conveniently store and carry these headphones wherever you go!

Features
  •  Great sound quality and bass response
  •  Hands-free headset for your phone and ipod and shuffle
  •  You can adjust volume by pressing + and - buttons
  •  Control music playback, answer and end calls, pause music, forward to the next song, etc. all by pressing the button on the mic.
  •  Standard 3.5mm earphone plug fits all MP3 players with 3.5mm jack
  •  Stylish design (non OEM) to fit your iPod, iPhone or other MP3players
  •  Third party product, not made by Apple
  •  Condition: New in Box ( as pictured )
  • Quantity: 1

Compatibility Information:

The remote and mic are supported by all models of iPod, iPhone, and iPad (not all models support volume up/down functions).

Audio is supported by all iPod models. Requires software version 1.0.3 for iPod nano (4th generation), 2.0.1 for iPod classic (120GB), and 2.2 or later for iPod touch (2nd generation).

Compatible with devices that support a 3.5mm standard jack.
